%BA%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B7%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31377","headword_ar":"اغتبط","root":"gbT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, regarded"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with unenvious emulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a wish for the like of his condition, without its being desired that it should pass away from him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in such a condition that he was regarded with a wish for the like thereof, without its being desired that it should pass away from him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Táj el-Masádir, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he rejoiced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became rejoiced, in being in a good condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in blessing bestowed upon him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was grateful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thankful, to God for blessing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounty, bestowed upon him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and the same, (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agobaTa","text_ar":"اَغْبَطَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igobaATN","text_ar":"اـِغْبَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the L, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a good state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition; in a state of happiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of enjoyment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wellbeing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiYa maA","text_ar":"لَقِىَ مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yugotabaTu Ealayohi","text_ar":"يُغْتَبَطُ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He met with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"experienced, that for which one would be regarded with unenvious emulation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a wish to be in the like condition, without its being desired that it should pass away from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fwz","text_ar":"فوز"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  The saying,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"xaw~aY qaliylFA gayora maA A@gotibaATi"},{"kind":"text","text":"cited by Th, but not expl. by him, is held by ISd to mean ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(referring to a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lay down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did so making his belly to be separated somewhat from the ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not"},{"kind":"text","text":"resting"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon a wide"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gabiyT","text_ar":"غَبِيط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but upon a place not even, and not depressed. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","L","K"]}]}}